Multiple runfiles

  Named runfiles in this directory will be blended seamlessly

Usage:
  run say MESSAGE [options]
  run server
  run [COMMAND] (--help | -h)

Commands:
  nb`say`
    Say something

  nb`server`
    Server management commands

Parameters:
  MESSAGE
    Message to say

Options:
  --color, -c CODE
    One letter color code [default: g]

  --help, -h
    Show this message